<law><law_id>710</law_id><section_number>12-2157</section_number><catch_line>STANDARDS.</catch_line><history/><order_by>12-2157</order_by><metadata/><url>/12-2157/</url><token>12-2157</token><structure><unit label="division" level="1" identifier="II">Division II - Planning and Development</unit><unit label="part" level="3" identifier="12">PART 12 - LICENSING AND REGULATION</unit><unit label="chapter" level="4" identifier="2">CHAPTER 2. - BUSINESSES AND TRADES</unit><unit label="article" level="2" identifier="F">ARTICLE F. - SHORT-TERM RESIDENTIAL OCCUPANCIES [7]</unit></structure><referred_to_by><reference>12-2156</reference></referred_to_by><text><section id="2077" prefix="(a)"><text/><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(a)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(a)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(a)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2078" prefix="(b)"><text/><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(b)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(b)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(b)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2079" prefix="(c)"><text>All sleeping quarters shall be served by working heating facilities and a bed with a mattress.</text><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(c)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(c)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(c)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2080" prefix="(d)"><text>The licensee shall meet each prospective tenant to determine that such tenant does not intend to use the living quarters for illegal activities.</text><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(d)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(d)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(d)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2081" prefix="(e)"><text>The licensee shall commence eviction proceedings against any tenant who engages in unlawful activity in or on the leased premises.</text><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(e)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(e)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(e)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2082" prefix="(f)"><text>The business location is not in violation of any applicable zoning, minimum housing code, and fire prevention code regulation.</text><type>section</type><prefixes><section>(f)</section></prefixes><entire_prefix>(f)</entire_prefix><prefix_anchor>(f)</prefix_anchor><level>1</level></section><section id="2083" prefix="(g)"><text>An up-to-date floor plan and current list of occupants shall be maintained by the resident manager. This floor plan shall be posted in a conspicuous location. 
